### Environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost/pet/public/
@json = application/json

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}animals
Accept: {{json}}

###

### List all animals (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/animals?limit=1&offset=0
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Filter animals by species
GET {{baseUrl}}/records/animals?filter=species,eq,dog&order=created_at,desc
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Retrieve single animal by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/records/animals/1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Create a new animal
POST {{baseUrl}}/animals
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Rex",
  "species": "dog",
  "age": 300
}

###

### Batch insert animals
POST {{baseUrl}}/records/animals
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

[
  { "name": "Mila", "species": "cat", "age": 2 },
  { "name": "Barko", "species": "dog", "age": 5 }
]

###

### Update an animal (PUT replaces all fields)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/records/animals/1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Rex",
  "species": "dog",
  "age": 4
}

###

### Partial update (PATCH only changes provided fields)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/records/animals/1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "age": 5
}

###

### Delete an animal
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/records/animals/1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Aggregations (count, avg, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/records/animals?aggregate=count:id,avg:age&groupBy=species
Accept: {{json}}

###

### OPTIONS preflight (CORS check)
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/records/animals
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type
